'''Unity Green''' was a large park on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]], erected following the culmination of the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]]. Removed from the rising skytowers of the planet-wide city, Unity Green symbolized the peace treaty between the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] and the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]]. [[Yorik coral]] bluffs rose from the shores of [[Liberation Lake]], while native [[Hawk-bat/Legends|hawk-bats]] preyed on bio-engineered [[yammal-jell]]s and [[coufee]] eels. The council room at the top of the [[New Jedi Temple]] offered a spectacular view over Unity Green. [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] was known to admire this vista before [[High Council (Galactic Alliance)|High Council]] sessions, and [[Chief of State (Galactic Alliance)|Chief of State]] [[Cal Omas]] considered it symbolic of his presidency.

